ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 19th day of April, 2011, the Motion to Defer Review to the United States Supreme Court or to Stay the Petition for Allowance of Appeal Pending Decision of the United States Supreme Court and the Petition for Allowance of Appeal are hereby DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
